    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Keys so constructed that the bit or portion that actuates the tumblers may be detached from the shank or handle of the key for convenience in carrying.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000038881/Stein, Construction Glossary (1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Llaves construídas de tal forma que un pedacito o porción que acciona los seguros pueden ser desmontados del mango o manija de la llave por conveniencia de transportalo. 
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sleutels die zo zijn gemaakt dat de baard of het deel waarmee het tuimelmechanisme wordt bediend, van de schacht of het oog van de sleutel kan worden verwijderd, zodat deze gemakkelijker is mee te nemen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>開啟制動栓的齒或部分即可自其柄或把手分開的鑰匙，以便於隨身攜帶。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
